</code></pre>



<p>This statement is information about the Intermediate Authority in “sub” and signed by the Trust Anchor in “iss”. A public key in this statement is the Intermediate Authority’s and signed by a private key of the Trust Anchor, like X.509 certificate.<br>The Intermediate Authority mentioned here is set up in the following step.<br><br><strong>Set up a mock server for Intermediate Authority</strong><br>Then prepare an Intermediate Authority as a mock server with two endpoints.</p>



