<p> <br> <strong>设置KeyCloak作为OpenID提供商</strong> <br>最终准备KeyCloak作为OpenID提供商：<br>首先，安装KeyCloak。下载并解开KeyCloak。</p>



<p> <br> <br> </p>



<pre class =“ wp-block-code”> <code class =“”> wget https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/keycloak/releases/download/25.0.5/keycloak-25.0.tar.5.tar.gz
tar zxvf keycloak-25.0.5.5.tar.gz
</code> </pre>



<p>接下来，安装KeyCloak OpenID联合插件。使用以下命令在目标目录中创建的JAR文件中创建的JAR文件为KeyCloak提供者目录。</p>



<pre class =“ wp-block-code”> <code class =“”> git克隆-b update/keycloak-25.0.x https://github.com/thomasdarimont/keyclimont/keycloak-oidc-federation.git
CD KeyCloak-oidc-Federation
MVN干净包装
</code> </pre>



<p>然后，启动keycloak。</p>



<pre class =“ wp-block-code”> <code class =“”> ./ kc.sh start-dev </code> </pre>



