<h1 class =“ wp-block头”> <strong>结论</strong> </h1>



<p>在本文中，我解释了如何建立依赖方的3-RD方与KeyCloak作为OpenID联合信任链的开放式提供商。</p>



<p>Currently in the Keycloak community, <a href="https://github.com/keycloak/kc-sig-fapi">OAuth-SIG</a> (a group whose activity is mainly supporting OIDC/OAuth and its related security features to Keycloak) discusses how to enhance  Keycloak to build the Digital Identity Wallet ecosystem, for which we believe OpenID Federation plays a至关重要的角色，我们正在主动将开放式联合会功能包括在KeyCloak中。</p>

